org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.timelineservice.storage.common

Interface Column<T extends BaseTable<T>>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplicationColumn, AppToFlowColumn, EntityColumn, FlowRunColumn, SubApplicationColumn

    public interface Column<T extends BaseTable<T>>
    A Column represents the way to store a fully qualified column in a specific table.
